{"tid":2259822,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國反制美國  要求六家美國媒體駐華分社匯報營運細節","createTime":"2020-10-27T06:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T07:28:02.000Z","uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9b54ec022d116af114fd7433b5290ea223c8e2fc","tid":2259822,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國外交部周一（10月26日）要求六家美國媒體在一周內就其在中國境內的運作進行匯報，作為五天前華盛頓將六家在美國境內運作的中國媒體列為外國使團的報復措施。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國外交部的聲明，受影響包括美國廣播公司（ABC）、《洛杉磯時報》、明尼蘇達公共電台、美國國家事務出版公司、《新聞周刊》、美國專題新聞社這六家美國媒體駐華分社。<br />\n<br />\n新華社報導說，中方要求這些媒體&ldquo;自即日起，<strong>於7日內，向中方申報在中國境內所有工作人員、財務、經營、所擁有不動產信息等書面材料&rdquo;。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">中國外交部發言人趙立堅在例行記者會上說，此舉&ldquo;完全是對美方無理打壓中國媒體駐美機構被迫進行的必要對等反制，完全是正當合理防衛。&rdquo;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n他還誓言，如果美方&ldquo;一意孤行，錯上加錯&rdquo;，中方將採取進一步的報復措施。<br />\n<br />\n目前美中兩國關係由於貿易戰、新冠病毒和人權等問題陷入建交40年來的冰點。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-us-media-war-2020-10-27/5636359.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fchina-us-media-war-2020-10-27%2F5636359.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=62c17cf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-us-media-war-2020-10-27/5636359.html</a>"},{"pid":"1bc4e86ef587e681b0edafc497fb3148af7f64f0","tid":2259822,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:20:34.000Z","msg":"驅逐出境<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99de22fc8c400cf3cd6a40abf70fba0376856ec7","tid":2259822,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bc4e86ef587e681b0edafc497fb3148af7f64f0","tid":2259822,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:20:34.000Z","msg":"驅逐出境<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:27:57.000Z","msg":"最好啦咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ebdb952c83bb16b4e9228d74fd618e8f80c931","tid":2259822,"uid":281189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"直接攪柒埋啲外資啦<br />\n總有班白皮豬未醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b219e611c8244816ac4cd33b30043ea619d1fc","tid":2259822,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"反制都要抄，支那copycat!"},{"pid":"5d32d7f9f26ac22a352ad71a9b92e1d9fcbc8d06","tid":2259822,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"升級升級升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n偉大祖國快啲開邪惡美帝波"},{"pid":"b19d3296b24da284eafa84d416880cc098b95db9","tid":2259822,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"今次又冇講石頭又冇講腳"},{"pid":"20730bee764a554f35d7f3a7c2d2277f198c545f","tid":2259822,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"睇來中共點都唔會讓步，又制裁波音又查傳媒，咁有自信同美國玩落去。"},{"pid":"665961e9676dd715c2413577d127ae15e045228f","tid":2259822,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"20730bee764a554f35d7f3a7c2d2277f198c545f","tid":2259822,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"睇來中共點都唔會讓步，又制裁波音又查傳媒，咁有自信同美國玩落去。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:21:14.000Z","msg":"加速師: 拖到我老友Biden上台就係美國讓步啦, 個陣我可以大肆宣傳美國跪低, 我戰勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3385da55325ee2436534928b7fece4582f0c7b3","tid":2259822,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"nyt cnn bbc 個渣<br />\n全部反trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f6f6c507573f4b73b0bd20b67fc8be2b89ae47","tid":2259822,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1